@startuml
title State diagram for the Digidoclocker class

[*] --> Unregistered : Open

state "Unregistered" as Unregistered
state "Registered" as Registered
state "LoggedIn" as LoggedIn
state "SessionEnded" as SessionEnded

Unregistered --> Registered : Register
Registered --> LoggedIn : Login
LoggedIn --> LoggedIn : Upload documents
LoggedIn --> LoggedIn : View profile
LoggedIn --> LoggedIn : Apply for certificate
LoggedIn --> SessionEnded : End session

LoggedIn --> LoggedIn : Continue uploading documents
LoggedIn --> LoggedIn : Reapply for certificate

LoggedIn --> SessionEnded : End session

SessionEnded --> [*]

@enduml
